        "subject": "LU-9836 scrub: 32bit hash for scanning lost+found",
        "message": "LU-9836 scrub: 32bit hash for scanning lost+found\n\nIt is strange that the readdir() triggered by initial OI scrub can not\nfind out name entry under non-empty lost+found. The reason is unknown.\nThe patch is for test purpose by replacing FMODE_64BITHASH with 32bit.\nLet's see what will happen.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <fan.yong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I5114421dd3d77a6b22ef72c8d4e3010f569d548c\n"
      },
